title.narrative: Effective & Efficient management of the Health & Nutrition programme

description.narrative: UNICEF Lao PDR efficiently mobilized the necessary technical expertise through staff and partnerships to provide strategic and technical advice and guidance to MoH and other line ministries and key partners, strengthen capacity, engage in partnerships, and effectively and efficiently manage the implementation of the Health and Nutrition programme. This has contributed to accelerated reforms in the health and nutrition sectors, to improve quality and address inequities. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
